easyrider/
├── __init__.py
├── config.py           # Configuration Module: Stores constants like field patterns and specifications.
├── data_loader.py      # Handles loading JSON data.
├── validator.py        # Validates field types, formats, and time chronology.
├── analyzer.py         # Analyzes bus lines, stops, and transfers.
├── output_formatter.py # Formats and prints results.
├── easyrider.py        # Main entry point to orchestrate the modules.
└── test_file_6.json

To test the refactored code:
1. Create the directory structure above.
2. Place test_file_#.json in the <easyrider> directory.
3. Run python easyrider/easyrider.py from the parent directory.